<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hollow1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hollow,</orth> subst. a cavity: <emph>love made those --s</emph> (dimples). <bibl n="shak. ven 243" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 243</bibl>. <cit><quote>into this gaping h. of the earth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.249" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 249</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the h. of thine ear,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.5.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 5, 3</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>by the happy h. of a tree,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.3.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 3, 2</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>